    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Simlarni Ulash Rejimi</h2>
        <p>● RJ25 bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>NSW Potensiometr Moduli RJ25 porti orqali ulanishi mumkin. Makeblock Orion-da RJ25 portidan foydalanganda, uni mos keluvchi portga ulashingiz kerak:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_potentiometer_rj25.jpg" alt="NSW Potensiometr RJ25 Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">

        <p>● Dupont simi bilan ulanish</p>
        <p>Dupont simidan modulni Arduino UNO asos paneliga ulash uchun foydalanilganda, uning OUT pinini analog pinga quyidagicha ulash lozim:</p>
        <img src="images/nsw_potentiometer_dupont.jpg" alt="NSW Potensiometr Dupont Ulash" class="img-fluid rounded shadow my-3" style="max-width: 400px;">
    </div>

    <div class="my-5">
        <h2>Dasturlash Bo'yicha Qo'llanma</h2>
        <p>Arduino Dasturlash</p>
        <p>Agar dastur yozish uchun Arduino dan foydalansangiz, NSW Potensiometr Modulini boshqarish uchun quyidagi koddan foydalanishingiz mumkin:</p>
        <pre><code class="language-cpp">
// Arduino dastur kodi
const int potPin = A0; // Potensiometr chiqishi
const int ledPin = 9;  // LED chiqishi

void setup() {
    pinMode(ledPin, OUTPUT);
    Serial.begin(9600);
}

void loop() {
    int potValue = analogRead(potPin);
    int brightness = map(potValue, 0, 1023, 0, 255);
    analogWrite(ledPin, brightness);
    Serial.print("Potensiometr Qiymati: ");
    Serial.println(potValue);
    delay(100);
}
        </code></pre>
